Well, I have gotten most on the bugs.  For the record, I counted from 
1001 to 1005 and that's how long it took to load my scenario 401 
(8000+ objects) to the point where you can edit in text on my PC.  I 
still got to work out a small bug I found in it about counting bytes.

Anyway, I am going to post what I have completed of text converter in 
the files section within 1-2 days.  It will only read information out 
of files.  I'll need to run quite a few scenarios through it before I 
am 100% satisfied with its ability to read information from scenarios. 
 It won't be fool-proof until I add the most of the functionality.
